{
  "stem": "26276.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whenever you looked out, you saw the same thing happen with no end, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a terrible, terrible place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't matter, because at the time, you just didn't care if you live or die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't ask questions, how or what, or when.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the only time that you knew that somebody is dying for a cause was when the one guy didn't show up back to work, to the camp, and they picked out every 10th person to be hung up.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And more than that, I recall on a Sunday, on a Sunday, we didn't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what we had to do was go out to the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know what would you call this-- it was like a place where you go-- not the bathroom, but they had made outside ditches, with a piece of, like, four by four to lean against it or sit on it.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So every Sunday, we would have to go out and clean out those ditches with buckets, bring them out, across straight to the field and empty them over there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one Sunday, we had to go during the day-- I don't remember if it was 1 or 2 o'clock, towards the kitchen window.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they made-- you know, Sunday you got dinners, like 12-- I mean, 1 or or 2 o'clock, to collect that.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
